        "Variables Description:\n",
        "The dataset contains 135 variables, but for our business objective, we will focus on these key columns:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Time Variables: iyear (Year), imonth (Month), iday (Day).\n",
        "\n",
        "2. Geographic Variables: country_txt (Country Name), region_txt (Region Name), city (City Name), latitude & longitude (Exact coordinates).\n",
        "\n",
        "3. Attack Characteristics: attacktype1_txt (General method of attack, e.g., Bombing/Explosion), weaptype1_txt (Weapon used), targtype1_txt (Target category, e.g., Citizens, Military).\n",
        "\n",
        "4. Perpetrator Info: gname (Name of the terrorist group responsible).\n",
        "\n",
        "5. Impact Metrics: nkill (Number of confirmed fatalities), nwound (Number of confirmed non-fatal injuries), propvalue (Value of property damage)."
